-- Algeria, Slovenia Tied 0-0 at Halftime of World Cup Group C Game
-- Peter-Joseph Hegarty
-- 2010-06-13T12:18:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-13/algeria-slovenia-tied-0-0-at-halftime-of-world-cup-group-c-game.html

          
          
             Algeria and Slovenia were tied 0-0
at halftime of their World Cup Group C game in Polokwane.  
 England drew 1-1 with the U.S. in the same group yesterday.  
 Later today Serbia plays Ghana and Germany meets Australia,
both in Group D.  
          
          


  


        